{"word":"G810 - ἀσωτία - asōtía - as-o-tee'-ah - Excess","slug":"G810","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀσωτία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>asōtía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>as-o-tee'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Excess"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C3;&#x03C9;&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03B1; - aso&#x0304;tia</b> - <i>as-o-tee'-ah</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G4982\">G4982</a>; properly <i>unsavedness</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>profligacy:</i> - excess, riot."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G811\">G811</a>"}]}